              <DefinitionShort>(a figurative extension of meaning of {L:γυμνός&lt;SDBG:γυμνός:000000&gt;}[a] ‘naked,’ {D:49.22}) easily able to be known in view of the fact that nothing is hidden</DefinitionShort>
